OL,3,CTravelodge offers flexible working in
OL,4,Crecruitment drive
OL,6,FTravelodge has launched a recruitment
OL,7,Fdrive to fill over 270 jobs across its
OL,8,Fbusiness.
OL,10,FThe company, which operates over 600
OL,11,Fhotels across the UK, Ireland and
OL,12,FSpain, employing more than 13,000
OL,13,Fpeople, said it is offering flexible
OL,14,Fworking, with the option to choose the
OL,15,Fhours and work that suits staff.
