OL,3,CTravelodge offers flexible working in
OL,4,Crecruitment drive
OL,6,FTravelodge has previously targeted
OL,7,Fworking parents who need flexible
OL,8,Fhours that fit around the school run
OL,9,Fand holidays, and students who choose
OL,10,Fto work at both their home and
OL,11,Funiversity locations.
OL,13,FJobs on offer include full and part-
OL,14,Ftime hotel manager and assistant
OL,15,Fmanagers, bar and cafe staff,
OL,16,Fhousekeepers, receptionists and
OL,17,Fsupervisors.
